18
00:02:32,923 --> 00:02:34,300
Drugs? What type?

19
00:02:34,383 --> 00:02:37,428
We won't know
until the lab results come in.

20
00:02:38,095 --> 00:02:39,346
There's one thing we can do.

21
00:02:39,430 --> 00:02:42,558
Get a sample of the exact beverage
