-Let's go inside.
-Sure.

37
00:04:27,746 --> 00:04:28,580
Sh!

38
00:04:45,806 --> 00:04:49,268
-Do you know her?
-I've never seen her in my life.

39
00:04:53,063 --> 00:04:53,939
Oh my God.

40
00:04:54,023 --> 00:04:56,650
-Uh…
-You don't know her at all?

41
00:04:57,401 --> 00:04:59,778
Like I told you,
I've never seen her before.

42
00:05:04,867 --> 00:05:07,661
-Not now.
-Oh, sure. I'm sorry.

43
00:05:08,162 --> 00:05:11,081
So when she kissed me,
this weird kind of plastic film

44
00:05:11,165 --> 00:05:13,334
came right out of her mouth. So strange.

45
00:05:14,543 --> 00:05:19,214
And then I suddenly got dizzy
and my legs gave out. Then I fell down.

46
00:05:19,798 --> 00:05:25,012
After that, the bitch dropped this liquid
right here in my mouth.

47
00:05:26,930 --> 00:05:29,350
Then she asked me some questions.

48
00:05:30,225 --> 00:05:31,143
Like what?

49
00:05:32,353 --> 00:05:33,937
You know, I… I can't recall.

50
00:05:35,481 --> 00:05:40,361
So it made you talk without
your ability to control anything, right?

51
00:05:42,029 --> 00:05:43,655
That's it. Just like that.

52
00:05:43,739 --> 00:05:44,948
Oh my.

53
00:05:45,449 --> 00:05:46,658
You're familiar with it?

54
00:05:46,742 --> 00:05:50,621
Oh yeah. So this drug
can make the user tell the truth.

55
00:05:51,705 --> 00:05:53,791
This drug is very powerful.

56
00:05:53,874 --> 00:05:57,044
It lowers inhibitions and forces you
to say whatever is on your mind.

57
00:05:57,127 --> 00:05:58,379
You know what else?

58
00:05:58,462 --> 00:06:01,340
