89
00:08:00,042 --> 00:08:02,586
-You ready for this?
-Yes.

90
00:08:03,504 --> 00:08:06,757
Well I'm glad you're ready.

91
00:08:07,257 --> 00:08:08,300
-Sir.
-Yeah?

92
00:08:09,009 --> 00:08:10,469
You can count on me.

93
00:08:10,552 --> 00:08:13,138
I'm much safer now!

94
00:08:13,847 --> 00:08:16,725
Looks like there are benefits
of hanging out with a champion. Hmm?

95
00:08:18,310 --> 00:08:19,436
Oh.

96
00:08:22,731 --> 00:08:26,568
Well, I guess now it's our time.

97
00:08:29,613 --> 00:08:32,199
NO CALLER ID

98
00:08:34,284 --> 00:08:37,913
You can answer it,
but you can't speak first.

99
00:08:48,465 --> 00:08:49,841
How's the president?

100
00:08:54,096 --> 00:08:55,013
Hey.

101
00:08:56,431 --> 00:08:58,016
What did you put in his drink?

102
00:08:58,517 --> 00:09:00,185
You're a fucking idiot.

103
00:09:00,269 --> 00:09:02,646
You still don't get it, do you?

104
00:09:02,729 --> 00:09:04,982
Want to know what else will happen
if you don't fight me?

105
00:09:05,065 --> 00:09:07,359
I will remove your coach's hand.

106
00:09:07,859 --> 00:09:11,321
I'll rip out your mom's tongue
and whore her out in Southeast Asia.

107
00:09:11,405 --> 00:09:12,281
Oh fuck.

108
00:09:12,364 --> 00:09:15,909
The president's cousin… I'll wash
that pig's face with hydrochloric acid.

109
00:09:17,035 --> 00:09:18,453
Go on, make me your enemy.

110
00:09:18,537 --> 00:09:21,081
Then I'll make every poor bastard
who needs money your enemy.

111
00:09:21,164 --> 00:09:24,459
That cop who got stabbed to death
right in front of you? Who did that?

112
00:09:25,377 --> 00:09:28,797
Just a coworker at his police station
who we paid 50 million won.

113
00:09:30,799 --> 00:09:32,593
Listen to me carefully.

114
00:09:32,676 --> 00:09:35,470
Everyone in this, world,
and I mean everyone, has a price.

115
00:09:36,179 --> 00:09:38,265
You'll get all the money I discussed.

116
00:09:38,932 --> 00:09:40,559
Just fight me one time.

117
00:09:42,019 --> 00:09:44,438
Shit.

118
00:09:49,651 --> 00:09:51,612
KIM GUN-WOO

119
00:09:52,904 --> 00:09:54,448
So that's it, you fucker.

120
00:09:54,948 --> 00:09:57,451
In a few days,
your coach's hand will be the first to go.

121
00:09:57,951 --> 00:09:59,119
Then your mother.

122
00:09:59,661 --> 00:10:00,579
Fun.

123
00:10:11,131 --> 00:10:12,382
I know his type.

124
00:10:13,842 --> 00:10:17,471
These people are horrible fucking vampires
who suck the blood from others

125
00:10:17,554 --> 00:10:19,181
and would even sell off their organs.

126
00:10:21,683 --> 00:10:23,352
If you want to take down a beast,

127
00:10:23,435 --> 00:10:25,937
then you need to be
a bigger, stronger beast.

128
00:10:26,521 --> 00:10:28,315
If you show the tiniest bit of weakness,

129
00:10:28,398 --> 00:10:30,275
