Get what I'm saying?

130
00:10:31,360 --> 00:10:32,611
What should I do?

131
00:10:32,694 --> 00:10:34,821
You want to beat the beast?

132
00:10:38,367 --> 00:10:40,118
Be ready to do anything.

133
00:10:40,869 --> 00:10:43,664
Like I told you, you must
make your heart as tough as steel.

134
00:10:44,164 --> 00:10:47,000
When your heart is steel,
then your fist is the sharpest knife.

135
00:10:47,084 --> 00:10:48,460
Then stab him.

136
00:10:48,543 --> 00:10:50,671
You have to take them down.

137
00:10:51,171 --> 00:10:52,339
Otherwise…

138
00:10:54,883 --> 00:10:56,385
